---
title: Hearty Roasted Chicken with Dijon Mustard Sauce and Green Salad
description: Nutritious, chewy brown rice is the perfect bed for this flavour-packed sauce. Our big tip here is to make sure you take the sauce off the boil and let it cool for a minute before you add the sour cream to make sure you don’t split your sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5888f3ae8e8c61312e536371-32cf5ae4.jpg
